
EXÁUDI nos, Deus, salutáris noster: ut, sicut de beátæ Terésiæ Vírginis tuæ festivitáte gaudémus; ita cæléstis ejus doctrínæ pábulo nutriámur, et piæ devotiónis erudiámur afféctu. Per Dóminum.
GRACIOUSLY hear us, O God our salvation, and as we rejoice in the feast of blessed Teresa thy Virgin, so may we be nourished by her heavenly teaching, and strengthened in the love of true piety. Through our Lord.
